<br>
I started my first magician the week the game came out.  By August, I was 50th level, and during that month I got my SMR.  I was jazzed... and after that session, ran over to Freeport to do some banking.<br>
<br>
As I passed WFP, I saw a level 1 mage just starting out.  They were standing in the newbie spot near the ogre vendor, twirling around and staring at things, as newbies of the time always did.<br>
<br>
I gave her my old robe... an Oracle robe that I had gotten quite some time before.  And, a brand shiny new dragoon dirk that I had just gotten from Dragoon Zyt.  I spent some time with her to teach her some basics of being a mage, twinked her with 20p, and went on to do my banking.  A day later, I had forgotten the entire incident.<br>
<br>
Flash forward 2 years.  I'd left and returned to the game, started a number of characters, and finally realized that the mage was my favorite of all, so I started a newbie mage.  I'm in Erudine, turning around and getting my bearings when a high elf magician stopped by and asked me if I was a newbie.<br>
<br>
&quot;Not really&quot;, I said.  &quot;I'm starting a new magician but I've played one before to 50&quot;.  We talked for a few minutes, and then he presented me with an Oracle Robe, Dragoon Dirk, Evil Eye Bag, 2 +4 Int Rings, a Crystalline Silk Sash,  a Loam Encrusted Amice, and some Wolf Fur Slippers.  <br>
<br>
He explained, &quot;A year ago, a magician gave me these items to help me start my mage.  He asked that when I passed them on, I was supposed to add another item to the package and give it to a 1st level magician to help them out.&quot;  He wished me luck and gated out.<br>
<br>
It wasn't until a few days later that I remembered giving out an Oracle Robe and Dragoon Dirk when I got my SMR.  I've always wondered since whether or not those were the same items I had given that mage so long before.  No way to tell, but I like to think that they were... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.showMessageRange?topicID=241.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.showMessageRange?topicID=241.topic&start=41&stop=52>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.showPrevMessage?topicID=241.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.showNextMessage?topicID=241.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=241.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.threadControl?topicID=241.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=241.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergoofystuff.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=241.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" ce